sequenceDiagram
  participant TF as Terraform
  participant Talos as Talos Linux
  participant K8s as Kubernetes API
  participant CI as CI (GitHub Actions)
  participant Git as GitOps Repo

  TF->>Talos: Provision VMs & Networks
  TF->>CI: Export Outputs (JSON)
  CI->>Talos: Apply controlplane.yaml
  Talos->>K8s: Bootstrap Cluster
  CI->>K8s: Install Flux/ArgoCD
  Git->>CI: Push Manifests
  CI->>Git: Sign & Commit
  Git->>K8s: Reconcile (GitOps)
